node.text: If you're building or renovating this is a kickstarter you have to check out! The future of showers. 2X more coverage using half the water of standard showers. This post is sponsored but I do use the @NebiaInc shower myself and am super excited for the next-generation! Check out the kickstarter via link in story & bio. #nebiabymoen
